items.badge_description: Denmark isn’t just the home of plastic building bricks, it’s also home to nearly 200 different breweries! Try 5 more for Level 11!

Wine isn't the only beverage worthy of pairing with a delicious meal. With so many styles widely available, there’s a perfect pint for any cuisine of your choosing. That's a beer at 30 different venues categorized as a Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 7!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 85 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 18!
99 bottles of beer on the wall, 99 bottles of beer. Take one down, pass it around.... That's 120 checkins with the serving style of Bottle. Try 5 more for Level 25!

Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 25 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 6!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 5 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 2!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 5 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 2

items.checkin_comment: Session Ipa con Simcoe, Citra y Mosaic. Pino, resina, tierra, fruta tropical, algo cítrica. Un poco apagada porque lleva tiempo envasada....
